snippet.title: Amber Heard Faces Marriage Questions As Johnny Depp Could Face Perjury Charges
snippet.description:
Wednesday, June 28, 2017 - Amber Heard arrives at LAX looking super fashionable in her sexy cropped leather jacket, semi-sheer sweater and high waisted trousers. The actress is asked if she has plans to marry billionaire boyfriend Elon Musk as her ex-husband Johnny Depp could face perjury charges for smuggling dogs into Australia.
